**Privacy Policy**

This Privacy Policy explains how personal data of users who use the **Coffee Fortune** application is collected, used, processed, and protected.

Our application respects the privacy of all users and operates in compliance with applicable data protection regulations (including GDPR and other relevant laws).

1\. Data Collected
------------------

Our application does not collect personal data unless it is necessary to provide the service.

The following types of data may be collected:

*   **Device information:** Basic technical information such as device model and operating system version
    
*   **User-provided information:** Identity details such as email address and name (for login purposes)
    
*   **Application usage data:** Screen views and usage statistics within the app (for anonymous analytics)
    
*   **Performance and crash data:** Anonymous error and crash reports collected to improve app stability
    

We do not knowingly collect personal data from children under the age of 13. If such data is detected, it is promptly deleted.

2\. Purpose of Data Use
-----------------------

Collected data is used solely for the following purposes:

*   Ensuring proper technical operation of the application
    
*   Improving application performance and stability
    
*   Detecting and fixing errors
    
*   Enhancing user experience
    
*   Providing core features such as login and account management
    

Personal data is **not sold**, **not shared for commercial purposes**, and may only be shared with technical service providers strictly necessary for service delivery.

3\. Childrenâ€™s Privacy
----------------------

The application is intended for a general audience and may be used by children. Accordingly:

*   No unnecessary or sensitive personal data is requested
    
*   No child-specific or targeted advertising profiling is performed
    
*   Personally identifiable data of children is not knowingly collected
    
*   Parental and legal guardian rights are respected
    

The application is for **entertainment purposes only** and does not provide real-life, medical, legal, or financial advice.

4\. Third-Party Services
------------------------

The application may use third-party services for technical functionalities. These services are governed by their own privacy policies.

Examples of third-party services used:

*   Firebase Authentication
    
*   Firebase Analytics
    
*   Firebase Crashlytics
    
*   Google AdMob
    

Advertisements are displayed in accordance with applicable platform policies.

5\. Data Storage and Security
-----------------------------

Data is stored on secure infrastructures, and appropriate technical and organizational measures are implemented to prevent unauthorized access.

Data is retained only for as long as necessary for its intended purpose and is securely deleted thereafter.

6\. User Rights
---------------

Users have the right to:

*   Request deletion of their personal data
    
*   Request access to their personal data
    
*   Obtain information about data processing activities
    
*   Request account deletion
    

Requests can be sent to:

**Email:** info@mesbu.com

7\. Policy Updates
------------------

This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. Any changes will be announced within the application or on the official app store page.

8\. Contact
-----------

For any questions or requests:

**Email:** info@mesbu.com

